# Quality Metrics Calculation

Calculate:

## Pass Rate

Formula:

Pass Rate = Passed / Executed × 100%

---

## Fail Rate

Formula:

Fail Rate = Failed / Executed × 100%

---

## Defect Density

Formula:

Defects / Test Cases

---

## Requirement Coverage

Formula:

Covered Requirements / Total Requirements × 100%

---

## Automation Coverage

Formula:

Automated Cases / Total Cases × 100%

